# Node Structure

```json
{
    "my_node": {
        "content": "# Title\n\nMarkdown content...",
        "level": 2,
        "position": { "x": 300, "y": 200 },
        "choices": [
            { "text": "Option A", "next": "node_a" },
            { "text": "Option B", "next": "node_b" }
        ],
        "resources": [
            {
                "type": "link",
                "label": "Learn more",
                "url": "https://example.com"
            }
        ]
    }
}
```

## Resource Types

- **link**: External URL (opens in new tab)
- **download**: Downloadable file
- **video**: Video link
